Danmann Bloodyback
Trade Skill: Brewer
Rank: High Council
Hello, I am Danmann the Bloodyback. I got the name once I perfected my backstabing skills on those pesky orcs in East Commens. After helping a fellow "darkie" kill a guard that started killing him for no reason whatsoever I decided to devote my life to ending those guards from killing any other dark elfs ever again. I began to venture farther from my underground home and out into the huge and dangerous world. I headed to the center of the continant, to High Keep and killed the pickclaw goblins untill I couldn't move because the loot weighed too much. And then I was finally ready to seek my revenge on the Freeport Milita. I made the long and hard trip back to East Commons and wrecked havoc on the weak guards that had once attacked me!
"If you turn your back on me,
you no longer exist."
